title: Dire need of a club looking for a jungler
body:
I need a club as I would like to play some games in which I play with people who understand my gameplay strategy and won't harass me... I'm a jungle main and my top champs list is given below. Although I'm lv. 27, I'm good at jungling and if you would give me a chance to prove myself, it'll be appreciated. Currently, I'm having great luck while playing as Rammus in the jungle...
